  <img src="http://cdu.edu.au/sites/default/files/newsroom/images/tasi_diak-300.jpg" width="300" height="250" alt="Dr Vannessa Hearman aims to produce a book about the voyage of the Tasi Diak" title="Dr Vannessa Hearman aims to produce a book about the voyage of the Tasi Diak" /><!--
