rmation and opening hours visit W: cdu.edu.au/artgallery. On Thursday, 8 March at 12pm the 2017 recipient of the Sulman Prize Joan Ross will give a floor talk on her piece titled ?The Claiming of Things?.<br /><br />It is a National Exhibitions Touring Support Australia exhibition developed by UNSW Galleries and toured by Museums &amp; Galleries of NSW. The National Touring Initiative is supported by the Australian Government through the Australia Council, its principal arts funding body, and by the Visual Arts and Craft Strategy, an initiative of the Australian, State and Territory Governments.</p><!--
