  <p><span style="font-size: 13.008px;">(From left): Dr Michele Willsher and Professor Sue Shore prepare for departure to Lao.</span></p><!--
THIS FILE IS NOT USED AND IS HERE AS A STARTING POINT FOR CUSTOMIZATION ONLY.
