  <img src="http://cdu.edu.au/sites/default/files/newsroom/images/belinda_chaplin-300.jpg" width="300" height="250" alt="CDU researcher Dr Belinda Chaplin is investigating the experiences of trans and gender diverse Australians living with HIV. Photo: Julianne Osborne " title="CDU researcher Dr Belinda Chaplin is investigating the experiences of trans and gender diverse Australians living with HIV. Photo: Julianne Osborne " /><!--
