  <img src="http://cdu.edu.au/sites/default/files/newsroom/images/fulbright-barra-300.jpg" width="300" height="250" alt="Dr David Crook will travel to the US to research fish migration" title="Dr David Crook will travel to the US to research fish migration" /><!--
