  <img src="http://cdu.edu.au/sites/default/files/newsroom/images/evolution_-_300.jpg" width="300" height="250" alt="Charles Darwin University evolutionary biologist, Professor Keith Christian. Photo: Julianne Osborne" title="Charles Darwin University evolutionary biologist, Professor Keith Christian. Photo: Julianne Osborne" /><!--
THIS FILE IS NOT USED AND IS HERE AS A STARTING POINT FOR CUSTOMIZATION ONLY.
See http://api.drupal.org/api/function/theme_field/7 for details.
After copying this file to your theme's folder and customizing it, remove this
